  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Digivolve] Lv.4 w/[SoC] trait: Cost 3[When Digivolving]
    By trashing 2 cards in your hand, delete 1 of your opponent''s 6000 DP or lower
    Digimon. If this effect didn''t delete, you may play 1 level 4 or lower [SoC]
    trait Digimon card from your trash without paying the cost. [All Turns] When
    one of your other [SoC] trait Digimon is deleted, this Digimon with an [SoC]
    trait Tamer card in its digivolution cards may digivolve into [Fenriloogamon]
    in the trash without paying the cost.'
